{"tid":1308033,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(絕食運動)又多一位巿民加入絕食","createTime":"2019-07-11T19:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T07:01:05.000Z","uid":171480,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cb49a945bb30d34825ca50b0fcd3280586dea481","tid":1308033,"uid":171480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JCQkody.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJCQkody.png&h=fdbd6e38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連埋呢位新加入一共有11個絕食者<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其中4位已經絕食<strong>超過200小時</strong></span></span><br />\n但政府同官員無回應過我地訴求 無關心過絕食者 <br />\n宜家部分絕食者體力都進入臨界點 好需要大家支持佢地既行動 協助絕食者 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">我們希望招幕每天的場地支援人員：<br />\n- 到場協助絕食者表達絶食行動的意念<br />\n- 派發傳單/叫市民睇日記等<br />\n- 情緒支援/陪伴到場又有情緒的市民<br />\n- 幫手紀錄每位絕食者的身體status<br />\n- 每日兩更：12:00-14:00/ 17:00-21:00<br />\n- 每更希望有3-4人</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">絕食者照顧team<br />\n- 早上了解絕食者狀況 <br />\n- 幫手清潔絕食者現場<br />\n- 陪絕食者去廁所<br />\n- 晚上9:00陪絕食者去沖涼<br />\n- 每日三段時間： 10:00am / 13:00pm-14:00pm/ 21:00-23:00pm</span> <br />\n<br />\n*不需要每天到，也未必要留一整更，但希望集氣，讓絕食者有更多支援～<br />\n<br />\n反送中絕食者分享tg<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/hungerstrike_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhungerstrike_hk&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0KGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=71faebdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hungerstrike_hk</a></span><br />\n<br />\n希望大家多d關心絕食者情況 仲重要係比更加多人知佢地堅持絕食既原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔可以浪費佢地既付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"070782596511e87ea3e7380b7e6cef81e95fb870","tid":1308033,"uid":171480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:09:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d483b37b2aff90f75be5f44dc85fb12a2236ef1","tid":1308033,"uid":171480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:10:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d34234ccb4e681de06d148197c95db7e9ae05add","tid":1308033,"uid":171480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3556c48a00b9b14205adb2d5227472e3ccb0a76","tid":1308033,"uid":250622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:10:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9e1f45113ac9a0dbf51f09c1dbdc8fffa375df0","tid":1308033,"uid":171480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:11:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d37668491b9fa93678c54eafd09364e189ceb629","tid":1308033,"uid":171480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:12:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&ldquo;當我們餓了，需要的不是食物，而是民意&rdquo;</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb70831d768f129e665af24fe83b2b3de66307f","tid":1308033,"uid":171480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:15:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f537f34d1303ce549e95d68867e09f10441bc94f","tid":1308033,"uid":171480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:15:36.000Z","msg":"就快十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87af5c90d8afd3944811fda92247eb0a71efdd31","tid":1308033,"uid":171480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"reply